solution: ```class Solution {
    public boolean canConstruct(String s, int k) {
        if (s.length() < k) return false;
        int[] freq = new int[26];
        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) freq[c - 'a']++;
        int odd = 0;
        for (int v : freq) if ((v & 1) == 1) odd++;
        return odd <= k;
    }
}
